306
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:34,510
He runs away so fast.

307
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,170
He doesn't answer my calls.

308
00:14:46,390 --> 00:14:47,220
Do you think he is

309
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,850
hiding something from me?

310
00:14:55,190 --> 00:14:58,090
Cheng, do you think

311
00:14:58,090 --> 00:14:59,370
