326
00:15:44,990 --> 00:15:46,580
It's all because they are young.

327
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:48,910
How many years can he be popular?

328
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:50,140
I just don't understand.

329
00:15:50,140 --> 00:15:51,110
Why can't he just

330
00:15:51,110 --> 00:15:53,490
