331
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:55,110
Is it that hard?

332
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:00,530
Stop drinking.

333
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:03,250
I just don't understand.

334
00:16:03,470 --> 00:16:05,630
Is it so hard to tell me clearly?

335
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:08,230
Why can't he make it clear to me?

336
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:10,290
I just... I don't get it.

337
00:16:10,290 --> 00:16:11,090
Why?

338
00:16:11,350 --> 00:16:12,540
I just want to hear Lian Rushen’s

339
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:14,250
explanation.

340
00:16:15,050 --> 00:16:17,730
He should just talk to me.

341
00:16:26,260 --> 00:16:29,040
[Mother]

342
00:16:31,540 --> 00:16:32,200
Where are you?

343
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:33,700
Why don’t you answer your phone?

344
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:34,760
I'm at home.

345
00:16:39,020 --> 00:16:39,770
If you're at home,

346
00:16:39,770 --> 00:16:41,050
why didn't you answer the phone?

347
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:44,000
I'm busy, studying, doing homework.

348
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,410
The day after tomorrow is the visa interview. Be serious about it.

349
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:50,860
Something came up suddenly.

350
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:51,560
I can't go there.

351
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,280
When you finish your interview,

352
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,250
call me as soon as possible

353
00:16:54,380 --> 00:16:55,170
