368
00:17:21,220 --> 00:17:23,160
Why do you have to disobey me?

369
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:25,050
Do you want to hurt my feelings?

370
00:17:28,040 --> 00:17:29,140
I hope this is the last time

371
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:30,200
you say this to me.

372
00:17:30,990 --> 00:17:32,350
From now on, the only thing

373
00:17:32,350 --> 00:17:32,920
on your mind is

374
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,330
to study economics.

375
00:17:34,950 --> 00:17:36,050
If you keep doing this,

376
00:17:36,090 --> 00:17:37,190
we'll all be embarrassed.

377
00:17:37,370 --> 00:17:38,070
Others will laugh at us.

378
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:38,950
Do you understand?

379
00:17:42,740 --> 00:17:43,920
I want you to think about it.

380
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:44,720
Don't be so naive.

381
00:17:44,980 --> 00:17:46,170
There is a limit to my patience.

382
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:04,960
Where is she?

383
00:18:05,970 --> 00:18:06,500
She drank too much.

384
00:18:54,460 --> 00:18:55,340
Why?

385
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:58,420
Why are you avoiding me?

386
00:18:59,910 --> 00:19:01,630
Why didn't you answer my calls?

387
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:03,960
Why?

388
00:19:12,410 --> 00:19:13,730
You bad guy.

389
00:19:13,770 --> 00:19:16,060
Why didn't you call me?

390
00:19:16,500 --> 00:19:17,690
Why are you avoiding me?

391
00:19:17,690 --> 00:19:19,230
Where were you the last two days?

392
00:19:19,230 --> 00:19:20,810
You bad guy.

393
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:23,050
Why are you avoiding me?

394
00:19:23,670 --> 00:19:26,750
Lian Ruoshen, you bad guy.

395
00:19:27,450 --> 00:19:28,380
Let me take you home.

396
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:29,260
I don't want to go home.

397
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:31,550
I want to drink.

398
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,090
Give me the drink.

399
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,020
Let’s go home first.

400
00:19:35,330 --> 00:19:36,210
I don’t want to go home.

401
00:19:36,210 --> 00:19:37,270
Don't you understand?

402
00:19:37,270 --> 00:19:38,370
I want a drink.

403
00:19:38,410 --> 00:19:39,110
Listen.

404
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:40,960
Let’s go home first.

405
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:42,020
Let's go.

406
00:19:42,410 --> 00:19:43,730
I don’t want to go home.

407
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:45,630
You don't understand, do you?

408
00:19:45,630 --> 00:19:47,470
Lian Ruoshen, I said I'm not going home.

409
00:19:48,930 --> 00:19:51,080
No. I want to drink.

410
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,280
Put me down!

411
00:19:53,810 --> 00:19:54,870
I won't go home.

412
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,650
You put me down!

413
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,070
Lian Ruoshen, put me down!

414
00:20:01,820 --> 00:20:04,370
I want to drink more. I haven’t drunk enough.

415
00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:07,760
I won’t go home. Put me down!

416
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:09,910
-Be quick.
-Please take care of her.

417
00:20:10,090 --> 00:20:10,620
Sure.

418
00:20:10,710 --> 00:20:11,230
Lian Ruoshen.

419
00:20:52,020 --> 00:20:52,770
What should I do?

420
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:55,890
As the clock is ticking, I love you
more and more.

421
00:20:57,520 --> 00:21:00,030
The happiest thing in my life

422
00:21:00,690 --> 00:21:01,570
is to love you.

423
00:21:20,010 --> 00:21:22,910
Put me down. I don’t want you to carry me.

424
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:28,850
What on earth do you mean?

425
00:21:29,690 --> 00:21:31,010
Now that you are trying to avoid me,

426
00:21:31,530 --> 00:21:33,070
why do you appear?

427
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,370
Why do you carry me?

428
00:21:37,650 --> 00:21:38,790
Put me down.

429
00:21:38,790 --> 00:21:39,980
I can walk.

430
00:21:44,780 --> 00:21:46,190
Put me down.

431
00:21:46,710 --> 00:21:47,770
Speak to me.

432
00:21:47,770 --> 00:21:48,910
Speak!

433
00:21:52,960 --> 00:21:54,410
Now that you want to avoid me,

434
00:21:57,670 --> 00:21:59,160
you should not appear.

435
00:22:01,670 --> 00:22:03,040
Otherwise, I will feel annoyed

436
00:22:05,190 --> 00:22:05,900
and sad.

437
00:22:08,100 --> 00:22:08,710
I’m sorry.

438
00:22:10,340 --> 00:22:12,010
I want to be a better man

439
00:22:12,010 --> 00:22:13,600
in front of your eyes.

440
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:15,530
I want you to see that

441
00:22:16,630 --> 00:22:18,350
I am better than you think.

442
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:25,080
Please don’t avoid me, OK?

443
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:28,600
If there is anything between us,

444
00:22:30,230 --> 00:22:32,690
we can talk about it. OK?

445
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:36,610
OK!

446
00:23:05,960 --> 00:23:07,980
[Cheng Feng]

447
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:25,050
Why do you come here?

448
00:23:25,580 --> 00:23:26,810
You knew I cooked

449
00:23:26,810 --> 00:23:27,690
the soup for you.

450
00:23:28,130 --> 00:23:29,450
But you didn’t have any.

451
00:23:30,110 --> 00:23:30,730
You were just waiting for me

452
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:31,870
to bring it to you.

453
00:23:32,840 --> 00:23:33,540
In the future,

454
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:35,440
don’t play such a trick.

455
00:23:36,010 --> 00:23:37,590
In case I can’t understand it,

456
00:23:38,030 --> 00:23:39,400
you will be disappointed.

457
00:23:43,050 --> 00:23:45,200
The room is so dark. Why don’t you
turn on the light?

458
00:23:50,130 --> 00:23:50,620
Cheng.

459
00:23:51,580 --> 00:23:52,330
What’s the matter with you?

460
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,610
Nothing. I miss you.

461
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:03,990
From the taste,

462
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:05,180
can you tell what I added to the soup

463
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,630
after you had left?

464
00:24:09,620 --> 00:24:11,740
Why did you add Hangzhou white
chrysanthemum and loquat?

465
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:14,380
Because you need them.

466
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:17,100
They can clear toxic material and moisten the lung.

467
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:18,640
They can also reduce internal heat.

468
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:22,250
Drink it before it gets cold.

469
00:24:22,820 --> 00:24:23,750
I’ll go back after you finish drinking.

470
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:30,920
My friend’s family

471
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:32,240
is so rich.

472
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:34,750
I can feel the pressure.

473
00:24:36,110 --> 00:24:36,810
This is not home.

474
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,570
This is a place I can stay.

475
00:24:40,820 --> 00:24:41,350
Dian,

476
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:44,430
do you have anything to say to me?

477
00:24:48,690 --> 00:24:49,880
I’ll show you my room.

478
00:24:56,090 --> 00:24:57,140
This is my room.

479
00:24:57,800 --> 00:24:59,210
I’ve been living in this room since
I was a child.

480
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:01,230
In this place,

481
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:02,770
I can be myself.

482
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:06,250
My mother has never taken much care of me.

483
00:25:06,870 --> 00:25:07,970
When I am ill,

484
00:25:08,010 --> 00:25:09,200
she just goes through the motions.

485
00:25:10,430 --> 00:25:10,690
[Feynman  Lecture Notes on Physics]

486
00:25:10,690 --> 00:25:11,400
But a long time ago,

487
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,590
she planned my life.

488
00:25:13,330 --> 00:25:14,700
She wants me to live as she wishes.

489
00:25:15,010 --> 00:25:15,750
Previously, I thought

490
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:16,460
it was maternal love.

491
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:18,130
Therefore, I tried very hard

492
00:25:18,130 --> 00:25:19,540
to win her attention.

493
00:25:19,850 --> 00:25:20,680
Later on, I found that

494
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,500
she only wanted to manipulate my life.

495
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,080
She doesn’t care about me at all.

496
00:25:25,870 --> 00:25:26,530
For example,

497
00:25:28,210 --> 00:25:30,800
my classmates’ parents would pick them up.

498
00:25:31,290 --> 00:25:32,910
She only sent a driver to pick me up.

499
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:36,210
She had never participated

500
00:25:36,260 --> 00:25:37,270
in the gatherings.

501
00:25:37,270 --> 00:25:38,410
Not to mention parents’ meetings.

502
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:40,610
Most of the time,

503
00:25:40,970 --> 00:25:41,540
I live alone

504
00:25:41,540 --> 00:25:42,900
at home.

505
00:25:43,430 --> 00:25:44,050
I think

506
00:25:45,670 --> 00:25:46,290
I’m used to it.

507
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:48,840
No one will praise me when my score is high.

508
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,340
No one will blame me when my score is low.

509
00:25:54,210 --> 00:25:55,620
Sometimes I would think

510
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:57,380
if I die someday,

511
00:25:57,380 --> 00:25:58,610
they won’t know it.

512
00:26:01,820 --> 00:26:04,240
Dian, although

513
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:05,740
I don’t know what happened between you and your parents,

514
00:26:06,710 --> 00:26:07,810
but no parents

515
00:26:07,810 --> 00:26:08,770
do not love their children.

516
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,410
It’s not that they don’t care about you.

517
00:26:11,990 --> 00:26:13,530
They just don’t know how to express it.

518
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:16,690
If they really

519
00:26:16,690 --> 00:26:17,880
don’t care at all,

520
00:26:18,670 --> 00:26:20,260
they won’t participate in your life.

521
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,720
Not to mention planning your life.

522
00:26:24,920 --> 00:26:25,490
Really?

523
00:26:26,330 --> 00:26:26,900
Of course!

524
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:28,180
I never lie.

525
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:30,600
Dian,

526
00:26:31,390 --> 00:26:32,230
why do you like

527
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:33,240
making paper planes so much?

528
00:26:34,730 --> 00:26:35,610
Because I hope

529
00:26:36,670 --> 00:26:37,950
my dreams can fly

530
00:26:38,250 --> 00:26:39,840
with the paper planes.

531
00:26:42,170 --> 00:26:43,050
But I...

532
00:26:43,050 --> 00:26:44,020
If you want to fly,

533
00:26:44,150 --> 00:26:45,070
you can fly at any time.

534
00:26:51,150 --> 00:26:51,590
Dian,

535
00:26:52,860 --> 00:26:54,450
even if the whole world doesn’t believe you,

536
00:26:55,460 --> 00:26:56,290
I would still believe you.

537
00:27:06,410 --> 00:27:06,900
Dian,

538
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,450
will you go to Hua City tomorrow?

539
00:27:13,670 --> 00:27:14,820
Shall I

540
00:27:15,610 --> 00:27:17,020
stay with you tonight?

541
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:54,460
Dian, you...

542
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:56,570
I know

543
00:27:57,410 --> 00:27:58,640
you want to comfort me.

544
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:02,030
I can’t let you make sacrifices.

545
00:28:04,100 --> 00:28:05,060
Take a rest today.

546
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:07,220
Have a good sleep.

547
00:28:45,850 --> 00:28:46,470
You are awake.

548
00:28:47,610 --> 00:28:48,840
Get up and have breakfast.

549
00:28:49,150 --> 00:28:50,120
I’ll drive you to the airport later.

550
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:54,210
Have you had breakfast?

551
00:28:54,390 --> 00:28:55,750
Don’t worry about me. You have breakfast first.

552
00:28:56,150 --> 00:28:57,420
I want to have breakfast with you.

553
00:28:59,360 --> 00:29:01,120
Can you drive me to the airport later?

554
00:29:06,140 --> 00:29:06,750
Hello!

555
00:29:06,930 --> 00:29:08,340
Cheng, where are you?

556
00:29:08,690 --> 00:29:09,610
A client has come.

557
00:29:09,610 --> 00:29:10,540
He wanted to make an appointment.

558
00:29:10,760 --> 00:29:12,250
They will organize a film-watching event tomorrow.

559
00:29:12,430 --> 00:29:13,700
There will be about thirty people.

560
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:14,280
They need us to provide

561
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:16,700
coffee, refreshments, sweets, wine,

562
00:29:16,740 --> 00:29:17,090
etc.

563
00:29:17,490 --> 00:29:18,760
It’s a big order.

564
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:19,910
I need to discuss it with you.

565
00:29:20,220 --> 00:29:21,450
OK. I’ll go back immediately.

566
00:29:21,710 --> 00:29:22,110
OK.

567
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,710
Dian, I have to go back to the bookstore.

568
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:30,910
Can you drive me to the airport first?

569
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:35,040
Be nice.

570
00:29:48,680 --> 00:29:53,000
[Domestic Departure]

571
00:29:55,370 --> 00:29:55,990
Enough.

572
00:29:56,910 --> 00:29:57,620
Let’s go.

573
00:29:57,620 --> 00:29:58,280
Stop waiting.

574
00:29:59,640 --> 00:30:00,870
There is a saying that

575
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:02,760
absence makes the heart grow fonder.

576
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:04,260
After a brief parting,

577
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:05,180
you will feel your love is sweeter.

